             were indicted for <rs id="t18220109-44-off219" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220109-44-off219" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220109-44-off219" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dweling-house, of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220109-44-victim444" type="victimName">
                           Robert 
                           Ray
                        <interp inst="t18220109-44-victim444" type="surname" value="Ray"></interp>
