                  ; four shirts, value 2 l.; six neckcloths, value 12 s.; one waistcoat, value 10 s.; one pair of breeches, value 10 s., and seven pair of stockings, value 12 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220109-44-victim450" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Harland
                  <interp inst="t18220109-44-victim450" type="surname" value="Harland"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220109-44-victim450" type="given" value="John"></interp>
