                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220109-44-defend440 t18220109-44-punish223"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 24.</p>
               <p>WILSON - <rs id="t18220109-44-verdict224" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220109-44-verdict224" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. - <rs id="t18220109-44-punish225" type="punishmentDescription">
